0, 103.0], [168.0, 101.0]]], "lines": ["課後５５乗っ取り注意"]}, {"box": [211, 304, 262, 356], "vertical": false, "font_size": 51, "lines_coords": [[[211.0, 305.0], [262.0, 305.0], [262.0, 356.0], [211.0, 356.0]]], "lines": ["む"]}, {"box": [622, 841, 682, 995], "vertical": true, "font_size": 60, "lines_coords": [[[622.0, 841.0], [682.0, 841.0], [682.0, 995.0], [622.0, 995.0]]], "lines": ["はっ！？"]}, {"box": [845, 1025, 1072, 1098], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32, "lines_coords": [[[853.0, 1027.0], [1065.0, 1025.0], [1065.0, 1057.0], [853.0, 1059.0]], [[851.0, 1065.0], [999.0, 1065.0], [999.0, 1098.0], [851.0, 1098.0]]], "lines": ["今図書室だけど", "どうした？"]}, {"box": [901, 1166, 1216, 1230], "vertical": false, "font_size": 29, "lines_coords": [[[901.0, 1170.0], [1213.0, 1170.0], [1213.0, 1201.0], [901.0, 1201.0]], [[901.0, 1203.0], [1055.0, 1203.0], [1055.0, 1230.0], [901.0, 1230.0]]], "lines": ["ちょっと手伝ってもらって", "いいですか？"]}, {"box": [898, 1304, 1220, 1368], "vertical": false, "font_size": 28, "lines_coords": [[[903.0, 1305.0], [1220.0, 1305.0], [1220.0, 1336.0], [903.0, 1336.0]], [[903.0, 1340.0], [1188.0, 1340.0], [1188.0, 1366.0], [903.0, 1366.0]]], "lines": ["今どうしてもやらなくては", "いけないことがあるので"]}, {"box": [168, 911, 305, 1346], "vertical": true, "font_size": 39, "lines_coords": [[[262.0, 911.0], [301.0, 911.0], [300.0, 1346.0], [260.0, 1346.0]], [[217.0, 913.0], [255.0, 913.0], [255.0, 1329.0], [217.0, 1329.0]], [[168.0, 913.0], [208.0, 913.0], [211.0, 1065.0], [172.0, 1065.0]]], "lines": ["これ、何年か前に流行った", "ＳＮＳ乗っ取りサギって", "奴じゃ．．．"]}, {"box": [798, 1438, 881, 1732], "vertical": true, "font_size": 36, "lines_coords": [[[843.0, 1440.0], [881.0, 1440.0], [881.0, 1732.0], [843.0, 1732.0]], [[802.0, 1438.0], [836.0, 1438.0], [832.0, 1614.0], [798.0, 1614.0]]], "lines": ["ん？何かこの文章", "見覚えが．．"]}], "img_path": "00167.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1350, "img_height": 1920, "blocks": [{"box": [866, 185, 1177, 262], "vertical": false, "font_size": 38, "lines_coords": [[[866.0, 189.0], [1098.